      "text": "PostgreSQL (PGSQL)\n\n- Stores persistent data (users,\norders, trades, listings)\n\n- Enforces data integrity &\nconstraints\n\n- Supports complex queries /\nreporting\n- Handles transactions for\nconsistency",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "mr6mZ13k-1FinincnNU0b",
      "originalText": "PostgreSQL (PGSQL)\n\n- Stores persistent data (users, orders, trades, listings)\n\n- Enforces data integrity & constraints\n\n- Supports complex queries / reporting\n- Handles transactions for consistency",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
