      "text": "Redis\n\n- Stores temporary / fast-access\ndata (caches, sessions)\n\n- Supports real-time counters /\nleaderboards\n\n- Enables pub/sub messaging\nbetween services\n\n- Provides low-latency lookups",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "0hj72CJYubix0gR_Irkfp",
      "originalText": "Redis\n\n- Stores temporary / fast-access data (caches, sessions)\n\n- Supports real-time counters / leaderboards\n\n- Enables pub/sub messaging between services\n\n- Provides low-latency lookups",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
