      "seed": 1989101876,
      "version": 1601,
      "versionNonce": 909768204,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1770231591234,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Defines the structured messages and\ncontracts used for communication\nbetween services.\n\nEnsures consistency, validation, and\ncompatibility of data across\nMarketplace, Matching, Ledger, and\nWeb Client.\n\nServes as the single source of truth\nfor data formats, so all services can\nexchange information reliably.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "yR43RwVDpLivyIR_2oYB_",
      "originalText": "Defines the structured messages and contracts used for communication between services.\n\nEnsures consistency, validation, and compatibility of data across Marketplace, Matching, Ledger, and Web Client.\n\nServes as the single source of truth for data formats, so all services can exchange information reliably.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
